iod 2022-2033, and the description of the project financing and financing of the project financing of the Republic of Lithuania for the period 2022-2033. The conditions and procedures set out in the Regulations of the Minister of Finance of the Republic of Lithuania and the Ministry of Finance of the Republic of Lithuania on the implementation of the European Union Funds Investment Programme for the period 2021-2027 and the Economic Recovery and Resilience Improvement Plan "Lithuania of the New Generation", as well as the conditions and procedures laid down in the legal acts of the European Union and the Republic of Lithuania referred to in these Regulations.</p>
                                            <p>The project aims to digitalize the company and implement e-sales transaction solutions DTS Solutions UAB is a company providing information technology consulting, information systems audit and software development services. One of the company's most expanding services is the sale of various IT services (hereafter: products). Until now, the company has only sold its products directly, its customer service processes, including product order management, have not been digitised, so current solutions do not allow employees to provide services efficiently; the lack of e-business transaction management (i.e. the ability to manage the process of buying and selling products via the internet, including product search, basket (order) creation, payment and order fulfillment and management, etc.), has limited the company's pool of potential customers, and thus limited the company's growth of revenues.</p>
                                            <p>In order to increase its competitiveness, attract and serve more customers more efficiently and expand its sales, the company decided to implement e-sales transaction solutions and sell its products using e-commerce solutions. This project is innovative in that it will develop an e-sales transaction platform based on cutting-edge information technology, providing new opportunities for innovative product sales.</p>
                                            <p>The project will enable the company to digitise its sales process, sell its products more efficiently, provide faster and better customer service, reduce the time needed to sell its products and serve more customers, which will lead to greater product availability and increase the company's revenue.</p>
